			<header class="entry-header">
			<h1 class="entry-title"><a href="https://evelyngeorneys.com/2023/02/05/geology-word-of-the-week-n-is-for-notebook/" rel="bookmark">Geology Word of the Week: N is for&nbsp;Notebook</a></h1>		</header><!-- .entry-header -->	<div class="post-image-link"><a rel="bookmark" href="https://evelyngeorneys.com/2023/02/05/geology-word-of-the-week-n-is-for-notebook/"><img width="1100" height="1467" src="https://evelyngeorneys.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/0f8de-img-20230204-wa0000.jpg?w=1100" class="attachment-independent-publisher-2-full-width size-independent-publisher-2-full-width wp-post-image" alt="" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://evelyngeorneys.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/0f8de-img-20230204-wa0000.jpg?w=1100 1100w, https://evelyngeorneys.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/0f8de-img-20230204-wa0000.jpg?w=113 113w, https://evelyngeorneys.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/0f8de-img-20230204-wa0000.jpg?w=225 225w, https://evelyngeorneys.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/0f8de-img-20230204-wa0000.jpg?w=768 768w, https://evelyngeorneys.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/0f8de-img-20230204-wa0000.jpg 1200w" sizes="(max-width: 1100px) 100vw, 1100px" data-attachment-id="10334" data-permalink="https://evelyngeorneys.com/2023/02/05/geology-word-of-the-week-n-is-for-notebook/img-20230204-wa0000/" data-orig-file="https://evelyngeorneys.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/0f8de-img-20230204-wa0000.jpg" data-orig-size="1200,1600" data-comments-opened="1" data-image-meta="{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}" data-image-title="IMG-20230204-WA0000" data-image-description="" data-image-caption="&lt;p&gt;My favorite type of geological fie