			<h1 class="entry-title"><a href="https://evelyngeorneys.com/2023/01/15/geology-word-of-the-week-l-is-for-luster/" rel="bookmark">Geology Word of the Week: L is for&nbsp;Luster</a></h1>		</header><!-- .entry-header -->	<div class="post-image-link"><a rel="bookmark" href="https://evelyngeorneys.com/2023/01/15/geology-word-of-the-week-l-is-for-luster/"><img width="1100" height="825" src="https://evelyngeorneys.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/fa722-pxl_20230116_002515994-scaled-1.jpg?w=1100" class="attachment-independent-publisher-2-full-width size-independent-publisher-2-full-width wp-post-image" alt="" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://evelyngeorneys.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/fa722-pxl_20230116_002515994-scaled-1.jpg?w=1100 1100w, https://evelyngeorneys.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/fa722-pxl_20230116_002515994-scaled-1.jpg?w=2200 2200w, https://evelyngeorneys.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/fa722-pxl_20230116_002515994-scaled-1.jpg?w=150 150w, https://evelyngeorneys.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/fa722-pxl_20230116_002515994-scaled-1.jpg?w=300 300w, https://evelyngeorneys.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/fa722-pxl_20230116_002515994-scaled-1.jpg?w=768 768w, https://evelyngeorneys.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/fa722-pxl_20230116_002515994-scaled-1.jpg?w=1024 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 1100px) 100vw, 1100px" data-attachment-id="10272" data-permalink="https://evelyngeorneys.com/2023/01/15/geology-word-of-the-week-l-is-for-luster/pxl_20230116_002515994/" data-orig-file="https://evelyngeorneys.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/fa722-pxl_20230116_002515994-scaled-1.jpg" data-orig-size="2560,1920" data-comments-opened="1" data-image-meta="{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;1.73&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;Pixel 6a&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;1673864715&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;4.38&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;570&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed