	<div class="entry-content">
		<p><figure data-shortcode="caption" id="attachment_10222" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-10222" style="width: 1034px" class="wp-caption aligncenter"><img data-attachment-id="10222" data-permalink="https://evelyngeorneys.com/2022/12/23/what-to-buy-a-geologist-for-christmas-2022-edition/pxl_20221223_011215183-mp/" data-orig-file="https://evelyngeorneys.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/29ead-pxl_20221223_011215183.mp_-scaled-1.jpg" data-orig-size="2560,1920" data-comments-opened="1" data-image-meta="{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;1.73&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;Pixel 6a&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;1671793935&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;4.38&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;91&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0.020011&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;1&quot;,&quot;latitude&quot;:&quot;-27.530797222222&quot;,&quot;longitude&quot;:&quot;152.96264166667&quot;}" data-image-title="PXL_20221223_011215183.MP" data-image-description="" data-image-caption="&lt;p&gt;This is a great time of year to buy some books for the geologist in your life! &lt;/p&gt;
" data-medium-file="https://evelyngeorneys.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/29ead-pxl_20221223_011215183.mp_-scaled-1.jpg?w=300" data-large-file="https://evelyngeorneys.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/29ead-pxl_20221223_011215183.mp_-scaled-1.jpg?w=1024" loading="lazy" class="size-large wp-image-10222" src="https://evelyngeorneys.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/29ead-pxl_20221223_011215183.mp_-scaled-1.jpg" alt="" width="500" height="375" srcset="https://evelyngeorneys.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/29ead-pxl_20221223_011215183.mp_-scaled-1.jpg?w=500&amp;h=375 500w, https://evelyngeorneys.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/29ead-pxl_20221223_011215183.mp_-scaled-1.jpg?w=1000&amp;h=750 1000w, https://evelyngeorneys.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/29ead-pxl_20221223_011215183.mp_-scaled-1.jpg?w=150&amp;h=113 150w, https://evelyngeorneys.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/29ead-pxl_20221223_011215183.mp_-scaled-1.jpg?w=300&amp;h=225 300w, https://evelyngeorneys.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/29ead-pxl_20221223_011215183.mp_-scaled-1.jpg?w=768&amp;h=576 768w" sizes="(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-10222" class="wp-caption-text">This is a great time of year to buy some books for the geologist in your life!</figcaption></figure></p>
<p>This year, I&#8217;ve decided to post another list of great books to buy for the geologist in your life. All of these are available as e-books, so they make excellent last minute gifts.</p>
<p>If you want to look at previous years gift lists, here they are:</p>
<p><a href="https://evelyngeorneys.wordpress.com/georneys/2010/12/04/what-to-buy-a-geologist-for-christmas/">2010  Part I</a></p>
<p><a href="https://evelyngeorneys.wordpress.com/georneys/2010/12/10/what-to-buy-a-geologist-for-christmas-part-ii/">2010  Part II</a></p>
<p><a href="https://evelyngeorneys.wordpress.com/georneys/2011/12/03/what-to-buy-a-geologist-for-christmas-2011-edition/">2011</a></p>
<p><a href="https://evelyngeorneys.wordpress.com/georneys/2012/11/20/what-to-buy-a-geologist-for-christmas-2012-edition/">2012</a></p>
<p><a href="https://evelyngeorneys.wordpress.com/georneys/2013/12/20/what-to-buy-a-geologist-for-christmas-2013-edition/">2013</a></p>
<p><a href="https://evelyngeorneys.wordpress.com/georneys/2014/12/10/buy-geologist-christmas-2014-edition/">2014</a></p>
<p><a href="https://evelyngeorneys.wordpress.com/georneys/2015/12/19/what-to-buy-a-geologist-for-christmas-2015-edition/">2015</a></p>
