<p>&nbsp;</p>
<p><strong>Book #1:</strong></p>
<p>The Floor of Heaven: A True Tale of the Last Frontier and the Yukon Gold Rush</p>
<p>by, Howard Blum</p>
<p><figure data-shortcode="caption" id="attachment_10208" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-10208" style="width: 324px" class="wp-caption aligncenter"><img data-attachment-id="10208" data-permalink="https://evelyngeorneys.com/2022/12/23/what-to-buy-a-geologist-for-christmas-2022-edition/floorofheaven/" data-orig-file="https://evelyngeorneys.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/5d690-floorofheaven.jpg" data-orig-size="324,500" data-comments-opened="1" data-image-meta="{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}" data-image-title="FloorofHeaven" data-image-description="&lt;p&gt;Picture from Amazon. &lt;/p&gt;
" data-image-caption="" data-medium-file="https://evelyngeorneys.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/5d690-floorofheaven.jpg?w=194" data-large-file="https://evelyngeorneys.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/5d690-floorofheaven.jpg?w=324" loading="lazy" class="wp-image-10208 size-full" src="https://evelyngeorneys.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/5d690-floorofheaven.jpg" alt="" width="324" height="500" srcset="https://evelyngeorneys.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/5d690-floorofheaven.jpg 324w, https://evelyngeorneys.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/5d690-floorofheaven.jpg?w=97&amp;h=150 97w, https://evelyngeorneys.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/5d690-floorofheaven.jpg?w=194&amp;h=300 194w" sizes="(max-width: 324px) 100vw, 324px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-10208" class="wp-caption-text">Picture from Amazon.</figcaption></figure></p>
<p>I read this book several years ago when I was working as an exploration geologist in Alaska, and I really enjoyed it. The book is well written and captivates you with a thrilling &#8211; and true! &#8211; story from the Yukon Gold Rush.</p>
<p>Available from Amazon <a href="https://www.amazon.com/Floor-Heaven-True-Frontier-Yukon/dp/0307461734">here</a>. $13.99 on Kindle.</p>
<p>&nbsp;</p>
<p><strong>Book #2:</strong></p>
<p>Earth: An Intimate History</p>
<p>by, Richard Fortey</p>
<p><figure data-shortcode="caption" id="attachment_10210" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-10210" style="width: 325px" class="wp-caption aligncenter"><img data-attachment-id="10210" data-permalink="https://evelyngeorneys.com/2022/12/23/what-to-buy-a-geologist-for-christmas-2022-edition/earthbook/" data-orig-file="https://evelyngeorneys.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/3e4de-earthbook.jpg" data-orig-size="325,500" data-comments-opened="1" data-image-meta="{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}" data-image-title="EarthBook" data-image-description="" data-image-caption="&lt;p&gt;Picture from Amazon. &lt;/p&gt;
" data-medium-file="https://evelyngeorneys.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/3e4de-earthbook.jpg?w=195" data-large-file="https://evelyngeorneys.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/3e4de-earthbook.jpg?w=325" loading="lazy" class="size-full wp-image-10210" src="https://evelyngeorneys.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/3e4de-earthbook.jpg" alt="" width="325" height="500" srcset="https://evelyngeorneys.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/3e4de-earthbook.jpg 325w, https://evelyngeorneys.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/3e4de-earthbook.jpg?w=98&amp;h=150 98w, https://evelyngeorneys.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/3e4de-earthbook.jpg?w=195&amp;h=300 195w" sizes="(max-width: 325px) 100vw, 325px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-10210" class="wp-caption-text">Picture from Amazon.</figcaption></figure></p>
<p>This classic book by Richard Fortey is an excellent read. I can also recommend his books <a href="https://www.amazon.com/Life-Natural-History-First-Billion/dp/037570261X/ref=pd_bxgy_img_sccl_1/133-2659009-6369753?pd_rd_w=ikVGT&amp;content-id=amzn1.sym.7f0cf323-50c6-49e3-b3f9-63546bb79c92&amp;pf_rd_p=7f0cf323-50c6-49e3-b3f9-63546bb79c92&amp;pf_rd_r=2T22Z94NH533P3ZZGY08&amp;pd_rd_wg=4b39N&amp;pd_rd_r=fa1a569b-b869-46d6-add4-02f63e25596f&amp;pd_rd_i=037570261X&amp;psc=1">Life</a> and <a href="https://www.amazon.com/Trilobite-Eyewitness-Evolution-Richard-Fortey/dp/0375706216/ref=pd_bxgy_img_sccl_2/133-2659009-6369753?pd_rd_w=ikVGT&amp;content-id=amzn1.sym.7f0cf323-50c6-49e3-b3f9-63546bb79c92&amp;pf_rd_p=7f0cf323-50c6-49e3-b3f9-63546bb79c92&amp;pf_rd_r=2T22Z94NH533P3ZZGY08&amp;pd_rd_wg=4b39N&amp;pd_rd_r=fa1a569b-b869-46d6-add4-02f63e25596f&amp;pd_rd_i=0375706216&amp;psc=1">Trilobite</a>.</p>
<p>Available from Amazon <a href="https://www.amazon.com/Earth-Intimate-History-Richard-Fortey/dp/0375706208/ref=pd_bxgy_img_sccl_2/133-2659009-6369753?pd_rd_w=iwygW&amp;content-id=amzn1.sym.7f0cf323-50c6-49e3-b3f9-63546bb79c92&amp;pf_rd_p=7f0cf323-50c6-49e3-b3f9-63546bb79c92&amp;pf_rd_r=5A4FW0F6VE52Y2X51JGZ&amp;pd_rd_wg=JGYYo&amp;pd_rd_r=492a5dba-ce81-49c2-b7fc-7b1e6ed9c4e3&amp;pd_rd_i=0375706208&amp;psc=1">here</a>. $12.99 on Kindle.</p>
<p>&nbsp;</p>
<p><strong>Book #3:</strong></p>
<p>A Portrait of the Scientist as a Young Woman</p>
<p>by, Lindy Elkins-Tanton</p>
<p><figure data-shortcode="caption" id="attachment_10212" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-10212" style="width: 331px" class="wp-caption aligncenter"><img data-attachment-id="10212" data-permalink="https://evelyngeorneys.com/2022/12/23/what-to-buy-a-geologist-for-christmas-2022-edition/portrait/" data-orig-file="https://evelyngeorneys.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/64b1e-portrait.jpg" data-orig-size="331,499" data-comments-opened="1" data-image-meta="{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}" data-image-title="Portrait" data-image-description="" data-image-caption="&lt;p&gt;Picture from Amazon.&lt;/p&gt;
" data-medium-file="https://evelyngeorneys.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/64b1e-portrait.jpg?w=199" data-large-file="https://evelyngeorneys.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/64b1e-portrait.jpg?w=331" loading="lazy" class="size-full wp-image-10212" src="https://evelyngeorneys.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/64b1e-portrait.jpg" alt="" width="331" height="499" srcset="https://evelyngeorneys.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/64b1e-portrait.jpg 331w, https://evelyngeorneys.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/64b1e-portrait.jpg?w=99&amp;h=150 99w, https://evelyngeorneys.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/64b1e-portrait.jpg?w=199&amp;h=300 199w" sizes="(max-width: 331px) 100vw, 331px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-10212" class="wp-caption-text">Picture from Amazon.</figcaption></figure></p>
<p>This is a delightful memoir by planetary scientist <a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Lindy_Elkins-Tanton">Lindy Elkins-Tanton</a>. I was fortunate enough to spend some time with Lindy when we were both based at MIT. She is an amazing woman, and you will enjoy her book.</p>
<p>Available from Amazon <a href="https://www.amazon.com/Portrait-Scientist-Young-Woman/dp/0063086905/ref=sr_1_1?crid=DV91PNQ0J2YC&amp;keywords=lindy+elkins-tanton&amp;qid=1671754206&amp;s=books&amp;sprefix=lindy+elkins-tanton%2Cstripbooks-intl-ship%2C359&amp;sr=1-1">here</a>. $15.99 on Kindle.</p>
<p>&nbsp;</p>
<p><strong>Book #4:</strong></p>
<p>Bright Galaxies, Dark Matter, and Beyond: The Life of Astronomer Vera Rubin</p>
<p>by, Ashley Jean Yeager</p>
<p><figure data-shortcode="caption" id="attachment_10214" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-10214" style="width: 328px" class="wp-caption aligncenter"><img data-attachment-id="10214" data-permalink="https://evelyngeorneys.com/2022/12/23/what-to-buy-a-geologist-for-christmas-2022-edition/verarubin/" data-orig-file="https://evelyngeorneys.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/f8238-verarubin.jpg" data-orig-size="328,500" data-comments-opened="1" data-image-meta="{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}" data-image-title="VeraRubin" data-image-description="&lt;p&gt;Picture from Amazon. &lt;/p&gt;
" data-image-caption="" data-medium-file="https://evelyngeorneys.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/f8238-verarubin.jpg?w=197" data-large-file="https://evelyngeorneys.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/f8238-verarubin.jpg?w=328" loading="lazy" class="wp-image-10214 size-full" src="https://evelyngeorneys.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/f8238-verarubin.jpg" alt="" width="328" height="500" srcset="https://evelyngeorneys.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/f8238-verarubin.jpg 328w, https://evelyngeorneys.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/f8238-verarubin.jpg?w=98&amp;h=150 98w, https://evelyngeorneys.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/f8238-verarubin.jpg?w=197&amp;h=300 197w" sizes="(max-width: 328px) 100vw, 328px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-10214" class="wp-caption-text">Picture from Amazon.</figcaption></figure></p>
<p>Here is another great book about an incredible scientist, the astronomer <a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Vera_Rubin">Vera Rubin</a>. Highly recommended!</p>
<p>Available from Amazon <a href="https://www.amazon.com/Bright-Galaxies-Dark-Matter-Beyond-ebook/dp/B08NT4JPS2/ref=tmm_kin_swatch_0?_encoding=UTF8&amp;qid=&amp;sr=">here</a>. $14.99 on Kindle.</p>
<p>&nbsp;</p>
<p><strong>Book #5:</strong></p>
<p>How to Build a Habitable Planet: The Story of Earth from the Big Bang to Humankind</p>
<p>by, Charles Langmuir and Wallace Broecker</p>
<p>&nbsp;</p>
<p><figure data-shortcode="caption" id="attachment_10215" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-10215" style="width: 329px" class="wp-caption aligncenter"><img data-attachment-id="10215" data-permalink="https://evelyngeorneys.com/2022/12/23/what-to-buy-a-geologist-for-christmas-2022-edition/habitableplanet/" data-orig-file="https://evelyngeorneys.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/25aee-habitableplanet.jpg" data-orig-size="329,500" data-comments-opened="1" data-image-meta="{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}" data-image-title="HabitablePlanet" data-image-description="" data-image-caption="&lt;p&gt;Picture from Amazon. &lt;/p&gt;
" data-medium-file="https://evelyngeorneys.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/25aee-habitableplanet.jpg?w=197" data-large-file="https://evelyngeorneys.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/25aee-habitableplanet.jpg?w=329" loading="lazy" class="size-full wp-image-10215" src="https://evelyngeorneys.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/25aee-habitableplanet.jpg" alt="" width="329" height="500" srcset="https://evelyngeorneys.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/25aee-habitableplanet.jpg 329w, https://evelyngeorneys.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/25aee-habitableplanet.jpg?w=99&amp;h=150 99w, https://evelyngeorneys.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/25aee-habitableplanet.jpg?w=197&amp;h=300 197w" sizes="(max-width: 329px) 100vw, 329px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-10215" class="wp-caption-text">Picture from Amazon.</figcaption></figure></p>
<p>This classic book, written by two famous geologists, is a must-read for any geologist. I first read this book as a graduate student, and I learned so much about the formation and evolution of the planet.</p>
<p>Available from Amazon <a href="https://www.amazon.com/How-Build-Habitable-Planet-Humankind-ebook/dp/B009GDH1NQ/ref=sr_1_1?crid=3GONLV9WT2YGW&amp;keywords=how+to+build+a+habitable+planet&amp;qid=1671755599&amp;s=digital-text&amp;sprefix=how+to+build+a+habitable+planet%2Cdigital-text%2C536&amp;sr=1-1">here</a>. $34.99 on Kindle. There is also an older, free version of the book <a href="https://www.ldeo.columbia.edu/~broecker/Home_files/How%20To%20Build%20A%20Habitable%20Planet.pdf">here</a>.</p>
<p>&nbsp;</p>
<p><strong>Book #6:</strong></p>
<p>The Dinosaur Hunters: A True Story of Scientific Rivalry and the Discovery of the Prehistoric World</p>
<p>by, Deborah Cadbury</p>
<p><figure data-shortcode="caption" id="attachment_10216" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-10216" style="width: 326px" class="wp-caption aligncenter"><img data-attachment-id="10216" data-permalink="https://evelyngeorneys.com/2022/12/23/what-to-buy-a-geologist-for-christmas-2022-edition/dinosaurhunters/" data-orig-file="https://evelyngeorneys.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/4fdb0-dinosaurhunters.jpg" data-orig-size="326,500" data-comments-opened="1" data-image-meta="{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}" data-image-title="DinosaurHunters" data-image-description="" data-image-caption="&lt;p&gt;Picture from Amazon. &lt;/p&gt;
" data-medium-file="https://evelyngeorneys.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/4fdb0-dinosaurhunters.jpg?w=196" data-large-file="https://evelyngeorneys.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/4fdb0-dinosaurhunters.jpg?w=326" loading="lazy" class="size-full wp-image-10216" src="https://evelyngeorneys.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/4fdb0-dinosaurhunters.jpg" alt="" width="326" height="500" srcset="https://evelyngeorneys.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/4fdb0-dinosaurhunters.jpg 326w, https://evelyngeorneys.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/4fdb0-dinosaurhunters.jpg?w=98&amp;h=150 98w, https://evelyngeorneys.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/4fdb0-dinosaurhunters.jpg?w=196&amp;h=300 196w" sizes="(max-width: 326px) 100vw, 326px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-10216" class="wp-caption-text">Picture from Amazon.</figcaption></figure></p>
<p>This delightful book tells the story of the rivalry between two 19th century geologists: <a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Gideon_Mantell">Gideon Mantell</a> and <a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Richard_Owen">Richard Owen</a>. The book also tells much about 19th century fossil hunting and interpretation.</p>
<p>Available on Amazon <a href="https://www.amazon.com/Dinosaur-Hunters-Scientific-Discovery-Prehistoric-ebook/dp/B00810SAWG/ref=sr_1_1?crid=GR7FILWXUT30&amp;keywords=the+dinosaur+hunters&amp;qid=1671756105&amp;s=digital-text&amp;sprefix=the+dinosaur+hunters%2Cdigital-text%2C518&amp;sr=1-1">here.</a> $8.99 on Kindle.</p>
<p>&nbsp;</p>
<p><strong>Book #7:</strong></p>
<p>Mapping the Deep: The Extraordinary Story of Ocean Science</p>
<p>by, Robert Kunzig</p>
<p><figure data-shortcode="caption" id="attachment_10217" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-10217" style="width: 370px" class="wp-caption aligncenter"><img data-attachment-id="10217" data-permalink="https://evelyngeorneys.com/2022/12/23/what-to-buy-a-geologist-for-christmas-2022-edition/mappingthedeep/" data-orig-file="https://evelyngeorneys.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/bd2af-mappingthedeep.jpg" data-orig-size="370,500" data-comments-opened="1" data-image-meta="{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}" data-image-title="MappingtheDeep" data-image-description="" data-image-caption="&lt;p&gt;Picture from Amazon. &lt;/p&gt;
" data-medium-file="https://evelyngeorneys.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/bd2af-mappingthedeep.jpg?w=222" data-large-file="https://evelyngeorneys.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/bd2af-mappingthedeep.jpg?w=370" loading="lazy" class="size-full wp-image-10217" src="https://evelyngeorneys.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/bd2af-mappingthedeep.jpg" alt="" width="370" height="500" srcset="https://evelyngeorneys.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/bd2af-mappingthedeep.jpg 370w, https://evelyngeorneys.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/bd2af-mappingthedeep.jpg?w=111&amp;h=150 111w, https://evelyngeorneys.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/bd2af-mappingthedeep.jpg?w=222&amp;h=300 222w" sizes="(max-width: 370px) 100vw, 370px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-10217" class="wp-caption-text">Picture from Amazon.</figcaption></figure></p>
<p>This is a fantastic, easy-to-read book on oceanography and marine geology. The writing is excellent. Very highly recommended.</p>
<p>Available from Amazon <a href="https://www.amazon.com/Mapping-Deep-Extraordinary-Story-Science-ebook/dp/B007XOPKS8/ref=sr_1_1?crid=29UN9RPVHV31R&amp;keywords=mapping+the+deep&amp;qid=1671757297&amp;s=digital-text&amp;sprefix=mapping+the+dee%2Cdigital-text%2C676&amp;sr=1-1">here</a>. $13.77 on Kindle.</p>
<p>&nbsp;</p>
<p><strong>Book #8:</strong></p>
<p>Missions to Mars: A New Era of Rover and Spacecraft Discovery on the Red Planet</p>
<p>by, Larry S. Crumpler</p>
<p><figure data-shortcode="caption" id="attachment_10219" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-10219" style="width: 398px" class="wp-caption aligncenter"><img data-attachment-id="10219" data-permalink="https://evelyngeorneys.com/2022/12/23/what-to-buy-a-geologist-for-christmas-2022-edition/missionstomars/" data-orig-file="https://evelyngeorneys.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/d1fe7-missionstomars.jpg" data-orig-size="398,499" data-comments-opened="1" data-image-meta="{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}" data-image-title="MissionstoMars" data-image-description="" data-image-caption="&lt;p&gt;Picture from Amazon. &lt;/p&gt;
" data-medium-file="https://evelyngeorneys.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/d1fe7-missionstomars.jpg?w=239" data-large-file="https://evelyngeorneys.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/d1fe7-missionstomars.jpg?w=398" loading="lazy" class="size-full wp-image-10219" src="https://evelyngeorneys.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/d1fe7-missionstomars.jpg" alt="" width="398" height="499" srcset="https://evelyngeorneys.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/d1fe7-missionstomars.jpg 398w, https://evelyngeorneys.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/d1fe7-missionstomars.jpg?w=120&amp;h=150 120w, https://evelyngeorneys.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/d1fe7-missionstomars.jpg?w=239&amp;h=300 239w" sizes="(max-width: 398px) 100vw, 398px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-10219" class="wp-caption-text">Picture from Amazon.</figcaption></figure></p>
<p>This is a great book about some of the recent Mars missions, written by a NASA scientist. A great read!</p>
<p>Available on Amazon <a href="https://www.amazon.com/Missions-Mars-Spacecraft-Discovery-Planet/dp/0063047365/ref=d_pd_sim_sccl_3_4/133-2659009-6369753?pd_rd_w=H7jSc&amp;content-id=amzn1.sym.cea269b5-2b99-44d4-a309-214a6674c0a9&amp;pf_rd_p=cea269b5-2b99-44d4-a309-214a6674c0a9&amp;pf_rd_r=093PCVJXDJVJYPW5RJ3Y&amp;pd_rd_wg=t8hIc&amp;pd_rd_r=2a721a38-9f94-49bb-8f78-411ed01c1567&amp;pd_rd_i=0063047365&amp;psc=1">here</a>. $14.99 on Kindle.</p>
<p>&nbsp;</p>
<p><strong>Book #9:</strong></p>
<p>The Red Planet: A Natural History of Mars</p>
<p>by, Simon Morden</p>
<p><figure data-shortcode="caption" id="attachment_10220" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-10220" style="width: 333px" class="wp-caption aligncenter"><img data-attachment-id="10220" data-permalink="https://evelyngeorneys.com/2022/12/23/what-to-buy-a-geologist-for-christmas-2022-edition/redplanet/" data-orig-file="https://evelyngeorneys.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/1bad7-redplanet.jpg" data-orig-size="333,499" data-comments-opened="1" data-image-meta="{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}" data-image-title="RedPlanet" data-image-description="" data-image-caption="&lt;p&gt;Picture from Amazon. &lt;/p&gt;
" data-medium-file="https://evelyngeorneys.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/1bad7-redplanet.jpg?w=200" data-large-file="https://evelyngeorneys.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/1bad7-redplanet.jpg?w=333" loading="lazy" class="size-full wp-image-10220" src="https://evelyngeorneys.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/1bad7-redplanet.jpg" alt="" width="333" height="499" srcset="https://evelyngeorneys.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/1bad7-redplanet.jpg 333w, https://evelyngeorneys.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/1bad7-redplanet.jpg?w=100&amp;h=150 100w, https://evelyngeorneys.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/1bad7-redplanet.jpg?w=200&amp;h=300 200w" sizes="(max-width: 333px) 100vw, 333px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-10220" class="wp-caption-text">Picture from Amazon.</figcaption></figure></p>
<p>This is another great book on Mars, written by a science fiction author (although this is, of course, non-fiction) with a Ph.D. in geophysics.</p>
<p>Available on Amazon <a href="https://www.amazon.com/Red-Planet-Natural-History-Mars/dp/1639361758/ref=sr_1_7?crid=2CX18DP7NKBHC&amp;keywords=mars+geology&amp;qid=1671757365&amp;s=books&amp;sprefix=mars+%2Cstripbooks-intl-ship%2C894&amp;sr=1-7">here</a>. $17.99 on Kindle.</p>
<p>&nbsp;</p>
<p><strong>Book #10:</strong></p>
<p>The New Climate War: The Fight to Take Back Our Planet</p>
<p>by, Michael E. Mann</p>
<p>&nbsp;</p>
<p><figure data-shortcode="caption" id="attachment_10218" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-10218" style="width: 323px" class="wp-caption aligncenter"><img data-attachment-id="10218" data-permalink="https://evelyngeorneys.com/2022/12/23/what-to-buy-a-geologist-for-christmas-2022-edition/climatewar/" data-orig-file="https://evelyngeorneys.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/02461-climatewar.jpg" data-orig-size="323,500" data-comments-opened="1" data-image-meta="{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}" data-image-title="ClimateWar" data-image-description="&lt;p&gt;Picture from Amazon. &lt;/p&gt;
" data-image-caption="" data-medium-file="https://evelyngeorneys.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/02461-climatewar.jpg?w=194" data-large-file="https://evelyngeorneys.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/02461-climatewar.jpg?w=323" loading="lazy" class="wp-image-10218 size-full" src="https://evelyngeorneys.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/02461-climatewar.jpg" alt="" width="323" height="500" srcset="https://evelyngeorneys.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/02461-climatewar.jpg 323w, https://evelyngeorneys.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/02461-climatewar.jpg?w=97&amp;h=150 97w, https://evelyngeorneys.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/02461-climatewar.jpg?w=194&amp;h=300 194w" sizes="(max-width: 323px) 100vw, 323px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-10218" class="wp-caption-text">Picture from Amazon.</figcaption></figure></p>
<p>Last but not least, I can recommend this excellent book on climate change, which discusses the role that big fossil fuel companies have played in climate change misinformation. This book is alarming, but also inspires hope. Michael Mann convinces you that it is not too late to avert the worst of climate change.</p>
<p>Available from Amazon <a href="https://www.amazon.com/New-Climate-War-Fight-Planet-ebook/dp/B088RN8FCF/ref=sr_1_1?crid=NTFS6482UHUS&amp;keywords=new+climate+war&amp;qid=1671757037&amp;s=digital-text&amp;sprefix=new+climate+wa%2Cdigital-text%2C724&amp;sr=1-1">here</a>. $12.99 on Kindle.</p>
<p>&nbsp;</p>
<p>Happy holidays, everyone! I hope you have a relaxing, lovely time with your family and friends.</p>
	</div><!-- .entry-content -->

